query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (chn.name like '%Aragorn%') AND it3.info in ('trade mark','essays','other works','LD contrast','taglines','LD analog left') AND (cn.name like '%Walt Disney Studios%' OR cn.name like '%Working Title Films%' OR cn.name like '%Warner Bros. Pictures%') AND it.info in ('LD sound encoding','color info') AND (mc.note like '%Mexico%' OR mc.note like '%Australia%' OR mc.note like '%India%' OR mc.note like '%Japan%' OR mc.note like '%International%' OR mc.note like '%Russia%') AND n.gender in ('m') AND pi.note not like '%R.E. Wells%' AND pi.note not like '%Volker Boehm%' AND pi.note not like '%Jillian Thomas%' AND (k.keyword like '%supernatural%' OR k.keyword like '%escape%' OR k.keyword like '%mafia%') AND mi.info in ('Irish Gaelic','Gujarati','Macedonian','Serbo-Croatian','None') AND t.production_year < 2008 AND (rt.role like '%Paul Hughes%' OR rt.role like '%Chris Kolaskos%')
